03:32.606 --> 03:34.472
You must be
Michael Westen.

03:34.474 --> 03:36.308
I'm Agent Pearce.
Thanks for coming.

03:36.310 --> 03:38.944
No place I'd rather be.

03:38.946 --> 03:40.078
Max was...

03:40.080 --> 03:41.346
A friend? I know.

03:41.348 --> 03:42.814
I'd, uh, offer
my condolences,

03:42.816 --> 03:46.017
but I'm much better at catching
bad guys than shedding tears.

03:46.019 --> 03:47.619
We'll find
whoever did this.

03:49.989 --> 03:51.256
What can I do?

03:51.258 --> 03:52.958
Let me walk you
through the scene.

03:52.960 --> 03:54.259
You be the killer.

03:54.261 --> 03:56.861
We found two bullets
out in the hallway,

03:56.863 --> 04:01.433
so if you're the killer,
you fire on Max out there, miss,

04:01.435 --> 04:03.001
then chase him in here.

04:03.003 --> 04:06.838
Blood spatter
says Max was...

04:06.840 --> 04:08.640
Where I'm standing.

04:08.642 --> 04:10.976
You bust in,
put two shots in his back.

04:10.978 --> 04:13.044
He bleeds out here.

04:13.046 --> 04:15.447
Now Max is dead.
What do you do?

04:15.449 --> 04:16.680
Run to the exit.

04:16.683 --> 04:19.317
I think you head
for the key log.

04:19.319 --> 04:21.519
So, you rip the hard drive
out of the wall.

04:21.521 --> 04:23.955
Now there's no record
of your entry.

04:23.957 --> 04:26.591
But how do you
get out clean?

04:26.593 --> 04:27.959
Elevator.

04:27.961 --> 04:30.428
No trace. Try again.

04:30.430 --> 04:33.765
I hope you're not asking me
to jump.

04:33.767 --> 04:36.901
Oh, you're the killer
in this little exercise.

04:36.903 --> 04:38.503
Is that how you escaped?

04:38.505 --> 04:40.038
Not unless I could fly.

04:40.040 --> 04:43.141
We found rope fibers, and I got
friction marks right here.

04:43.143 --> 04:46.011
The killer rappelled down.
Probably had help.

04:46.013 --> 04:47.345
How are your
climbing skills?

04:47.347 --> 04:50.215
Not bad. Why?

04:50.217 --> 04:51.716
Am I a suspect?

04:51.718 --> 04:52.984
To be honest,

04:52.986 --> 04:55.186
when I heard a burned spy
was mixed up with Max,

04:55.188 --> 04:58.156
my first instinct was to fit you
for a head bag.

04:58.158 --> 04:59.491
I appreciate
your restraint.

04:59.493 --> 05:00.992
Well, you <i>did</i> show up today.

05:00.994 --> 05:03.028
And as your new
agency contact,

05:03.030 --> 05:06.131
a head bag wouldn't have started
us off on the right foot.

05:06.133 --> 05:07.599
You're Max's replacement?

05:07.601 --> 05:09.167
We worked on some operations
together.

05:09.169 --> 05:11.536
I have some
investigations experience.

05:13.005 --> 05:15.273
I asked
for this assignment.

05:15.275 --> 05:17.242
Max was one
of the good guys.

05:17.244 --> 05:20.111
I want to find out who did this
just as much as you do.

05:20.113 --> 05:22.313
I'd love to have you
on the team.

05:22.315 --> 05:24.182
You should know this
about me, though --

05:24.184 --> 05:26.618
I've got a pit bull at home,

05:26.620 --> 05:29.120
and I learned how to run
an investigation from her.

05:29.122 --> 05:32.123
She sinks her teeth in,
she doesn't let go.

05:32.125 --> 05:33.892
Ever.

05:35.061 --> 05:36.661
She sounds like a nice dog.

05:36.663 --> 05:37.595
She can be.

05:40.132 --> 05:43.968
But she is a very,
very determined bitch

05:43.970 --> 05:46.104
when she wants something.

05:46.106 --> 05:48.540
I need to know
I can count on you.

05:48.542 --> 05:49.841
I'm your man.

05:49.843 --> 05:52.510
I was hoping you'd say that,
Michael.

05:52.535 --> 05:56.535
<font color=#00FF00>Burn Notice 5x05</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Square One</font>
